      "text": "ん……頑張る",
      "translations": {
        "en": "….Yeah‚ I’ll do my best.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.20535141626994,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 21.637301508585576
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あははっ！ 仲がいいですねー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha! What a supportive group!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.637301508585615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それじゃあ……ずばり、アイドルを目指した理由は？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then… my question is‚ why did you want to become an idol.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.137301508585615,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_08-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "…………好き、だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because… I like idols.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.57063484191895,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 29.570634841918988
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 32.40396817525229
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 32.47063484191895
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ふむふむ、好きだから……",
