      "text": "（……うーん。これも雫の個性とはいえ）\n（ 会話がなかなか弾まないな……表情も相変わらずだし）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Hmm… Shizuku’s unique personality aside‚）\n（the conversation isn't smooth… and her expression is the same as always.）",
        "id": ""
