      "text": "千紗、落ち着いて\n驚き過ぎよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Calm down‚ Chisa.\nYou’re overreacting.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 69.82646251122162,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_08-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ご、ごめんなさい……\nも、もう、大丈夫です",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ s-sorry…\nI-I’m fine now.",
        "id": ""
