      "startTime": 73.72646251122163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 76.92646251122163
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "驚かせちゃってごめんね……それじゃあまずは",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So sorry for startling you… Well then‚ first of all‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 76.92646251122163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "アイドルを目指した理由から教えてもらえますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "can you tell me why you wanted to become an idol?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.59312917788829,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 84.55979584455496
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_08-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "あの、その……お、お姉……ん……が……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Um‚ well… m-my b-big s-sister…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.55979584455496,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 90.65979574918752
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "……ああ、えっとー……マ、マイク遠いかなぁ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ um… the mic is a bit far.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.65979574918752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "speakerNameEn": "Host",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ごめんなさい、もう一回お願いできます？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Could you please repeat that again?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.59312908252092,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hoshistage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "01-2d",
      "startTime": 99.99312908252091
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_08/sud_vo_adv_main_01_07_08-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "す、すす、すみません！！\nその、お、お姉ちゃんが――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-s-sorry!\nYou see‚ m-my sister――",
        "id": ""
